('0905993', 'Nurfadilah Tri Astuti', 'The Implementation of Orton-Gillingham Method in Teaching Early Reading to Young Learners', 'Pendidikan Bahasa Inggris', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN BAHASA DAN SASTRA', 'Prof. Dr. Didi Suherdi, M.Ed.', 'Pupung Purnawarman, M.S.Ed., Ph.D.', 'The title of this research is The Implementation of Orton-Gillingham Method in Teaching Early Speaking to Young Learners. The focus of this research was to investigate the effectiveness of Orton-Gillingham method in teaching early reading, especially to improve young learners'' abilities in aalphabetical principles, phonic, vocabulary and oral languange.\r\nQuasi-experimental design was employed in this research. The participants of this research were two classes which served as an experimental and control group. The experimental group was given several treatments, while the control group was not given any treatment. At the beginning of the research, both groups were given pretest, in order to measure the students'' initial ability in early reading. In the end, post test was administered in order to find out if there any significance differences between the pretest and post-test. Then, t-test proce...'),
