('0906833', 'Sinta Ferlianty', 'Teachers'' Perceptions towards the Use of Authentic Materials in EFL Classroom', 'Pendidikan Bahasa Inggris', 'FAKULTAS PENDIDIKAN BAHASA DAN SASTRA', 'Prof. Dr. Didi Suherdi, M.Ed.', 'Sri Harto, M.Pd.', 'This research entitled Teachers'' Perceptions towards the Use of Authentic Materials in EFL Classroom, aims to find out teachers'' perceptions towards the use of authentic materials and teachers'' difficulty in using authentic materials in EFL classroom. The participants of this study were two EFL teachers who taught XI graders in one of senior high schools in Bandung. The method used in this research was descriptive qualitative. This method allowed the researcher to analyze, categorize and interpreted the data. In describing the findings, descriptive method was also applied by attaching simple statistical data and charts. The data were gathered by conducting observation, giving Likert-scale questionnaire, and interviewing the participants. Based on the questionnaire classification scoring, the results indicated that one of the participants showed extremely positive responses and the rest gave pos...'),
